<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
<title>Pumkhata A Siem Ahiu</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ma khan Eden huon thiengtho
 Mun hawih leh nuom taka khan
 Ei suonte Evi leh Adamte chu
 Chung Pathien guot bang zelin
 Nupan tuok khat hung suokin pumkhata siem a hiu

[V2]
 Lawptak in kipahpih hitiu
 I suohpih teu nupan hi
 Pathien in vangpie hen la veng bit zel hen
 A khawvel damlai niu a beih masieh in.

[V3]
 2. Chunga Pathien samsuih in
 Pumkhat in a kisiem ui
 Lal ma ah khenloh thimthu kitiem ui
 Tichun Pa deih lam guolin
 Dah leh nawpsak lai in le a thutiem uh det hen

[V4]
 3. Lalpa ka hun vawpsak ui
 Ka suohpih teu nupan hi
 Damlai go lul vangsakna hun pien la
 Amau di'n ni bang vakin
 A damlai niu a tum tieng leh Na kawmah puiin.</lyrics>
</song>